  "prompt": "What are the best documentary websites?",
  "response": "There are several excellent documentary websites that cater to various interests and provide high-quality content. Here are some of the best ones:\n\n1. **Documentary Heaven**\n   - URL: [documentaryheaven.com](https://www.documentaryheaven.com)\n   - Overview: Offers a vast collection of free documentaries across various genres, including history, science, technology, and more.\n\n2. **Top Documentary Films**\n   - URL: [topdocumentaryfilms.com](https://topdocumentaryfilms.com)\n   - Overview: Features a wide range of documentaries on different topics, along with reviews and ratings.\n\n3. **PBS Documentary**\n   - URL: [pbs.org](https://www.pbs.org)\n   - Overview: PBS offers a variety of high-quality documentaries on topics such as history, nature, and current events, many of which are available for free streaming.\n\n4. **Netflix Documentary Section**\n   - URL: [netflix.com](https://www.netflix.com)\n   - Overview: Netflix has a dedicated section for documentaries, including critically acclaimed titles like \"Making a Murderer,\" \"The Social Dilemma,\" and \"Our Planet.\"\n\n5. **BBC Documentaries**\n   - URL: [bbc.co.uk](https://www.bbc.co.uk)\n   - Overview: The BBC offers a range of well-produced documentaries on nature, history, and current affairs, many of which are available on their iPlayer platform.\n\n6. **National Geographic Documentary Films**\n   - URL: [nationalgeographic.com](https://www.nationalgeographic.com)\n   - Overview: Known for its breathtaking nature documentaries, National Geographic also covers scientific and cultural topics.\n\n7. **YouTube**\n   - URL: [youtube.com](https://www.youtube.com)\n   - Overview: YouTube hosts a vast array of documentary content from both mainstream and independent creators. Channels like \"VICE,\" \"TED-Ed,\" and \"Kurzgesagt \u2013 In a Nutshell\" offer high-quality documentaries.\n\n8. **Kanopy**\n   - URL: [kanopy.com](https://www.kanopy.com)\n   - Overview: Available through many public libraries and universities, Kanopy offers a wide range of documentaries, including many independent and international titles.\n\n9. **CuriosityStream**\n   - URL: [curiositystream.com](https://www.curiositystream.com)\n   - Overview: A subscription-based service that offers a wide variety of documentaries on science, history, technology, and more.\n\n10. **DocuBay**\n    - URL: [docubay.com](https://www.docubay.com)\n    - Overview: A subscription-based platform that offers a curated selection of documentaries from around the world, focusing on unique and untold stories.\n\nThese platforms provide a wealth of documentary content, catering to diverse interests and preferences. Whether you're looking for free options or are willing to subscribe for premium content, there's something for everyone.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
